query:
INSERT INTO task_templates (id, group_id, template_name, template_title, ticket_title, ticket_description)
               VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6)
               RETURNING 
                   id as "id!: Uuid", 
                   group_id as "group_id: Uuid",
                   template_name,
                   template_title,
                   ticket_title,
                   ticket_description,
                   created_at as "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>", 
                   updated_at as "updated_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
